  "body": "#### System information\r\n\r\nGeth version: `1.58`\r\nOS & Version: Windows 10\r\n\r\n#### Expected behaviour\r\n\r\nWhen doing a transaction between 2 wallets, I expect the balance to be updated\r\n\r\n#### Actual behaviour\r\n\r\nWhen doing a transaction, \"destination\" balance is stuck to 0\r\n\r\n#### Steps to reproduce the behaviour\r\n\r\nI first start a server in dev mode : \r\ngeth --dev --datadir C:\\tmp\\ethereum-test --rpcapi personal,db,eth,net,web3 --rpc\r\n\r\nI then start mining with a first wallet : \r\ngeth --dev attach\r\npersonal.newAccount(\"password\");\r\nprimary = eth.accounts[0];\r\nbalance = web3.fromWei(eth.getBalance(primary), \"ether\");\r\nminer.setEtherbase(primary);\r\nminer.start(4);\r\nadmin.sleepBlocks(10);\r\nminer.stop();\r\nbalance = web3.fromWei(eth.getBalance(primary), \"ether\");\r\n==> 50\r\n\r\nI create a second wallet and do a transaction : \r\n\r\npersonal.newAccount(\"password\");\r\nfrom = eth.accounts[0];\r\npersonal.unlockAccount(from, \"password\");\r\nweb3.fromWei(eth.getBalance(from));\r\n\r\nto = eth.accounts[1];\r\nweb3.fromWei(eth.getBalance(to));\r\n\r\namount = web3.toWei(1, \"ether\");\r\neth.sendTransaction({from: from, to: to, value: amount});\r\n\r\nweb3.fromWei(eth.getBalance(to));\r\n\r\n==> 0\r\n\r\nA friend on Mac does the same thing and it works.\r\n\r\nAm I doing something wrong ?\r\n\r\nThank's in advance\r\n\r\n#### Backtrace\r\n\r\n````\r\neth.getTransaction(\"0xca2b880a4abe819db00f37be84e91dd56967d87a5d3944753e0c4388c6f02c5c\")\r\n{\r\n  blockHash: \"0x445f054447e12b9a38689467991ac8dfa89b27a66dbbc0e3b5e9a5ce6edae03f\",\r\n  blockNumber: 15,\r\n  from: \"0x3a10c3df6110923cf1073c2263891be2793dd779\",\r\n  gas: 90000,\r\n  gasPrice: 20000000000,\r\n  hash: \"0xca2b880a4abe819db00f37be84e91dd56967d87a5d3944753e0c4388c6f02c5c\",\r\n  input: \"0x\",\r\n  nonce: 1,\r\n  r: \"0xf2a7f7ba6cfdc9c158d15b5701f417fc81b521fe672ae33f1bf1675f5cce5f86\",\r\n  s: \"0x40b6857046bb51387d622d5e72fb31b1b70fa57d63f5408e53333014edfbda98\",\r\n  to: \"0x0c3fcb964babbd419c71a3f488b746e365bc9683\",\r\n  transactionIndex: 0,\r\n  v: \"0x1c\",\r\n  value: 1000000000000000000\r\n}\r\n````\r\n",
